# AI API keys (optional for MVP — mock hints work without any key)
# Pick one provider, add the key, and restart the dev server.

# Recommended free tier: Groq (https://console.groq.com/keys)
# Model: llama-3.3-70b-versatile | 1,000 requests/day, no credit card
GROQ_API_KEY=

